<topic template="Default" status="Needs Review" modified="2026-04-29T14:05:39.332Z" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>3A.3 确认托盘编号</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">3A.3 确认托盘编号</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Confirming Pallet No..png" scale="30.00%" width="302" height="27" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">该字段显示工作台一侧的托盘编号。关于工作台一侧,</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:11px;">CW (LS103) 信号亮起，则工作台一侧的托板为 &apos;1&apos;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">CCW (LS102) 信号亮起，则工作台一侧的托板为 &apos;2&apos;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">当 APC 操作进行中，信号 LS102 / LS103 均为 &apos;0&apos; 时，托盘号显示屏将显示 &apos;0&apos;。</para>
  </body>
</topic>
